<div class="content-box">
    <h2>About Helping Hands</h2>
    <p>
        Helping Hands is a non-profit organization dedicated to improving lives by connecting resources with those in need.
        Since our inception, we have focused on facilitating community-driven efforts such as food distribution, education support,
        and disaster relief programs. Our mission is to empower individuals to build stronger, more resilient communities.
    </p>
    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
    <p>
        A world where everyone has access to basic necessities, opportunities for growth, and a supportive community to rely on.
    </p>
    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>
        To bridge the gap between resources and those in need by mobilizing communities, creating impactful programs,
        and fostering long-term solutions for a better future.
    </p>
